Welcome to NukeTracker, a player tracking utility bot designed for ARK: Survival Ascended. By using NukeTracker in your Discord server, you agree to the following terms:

1. Acceptance of Terms
By adding or using NukeTracker, you and your server members agree to these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, do not use the bot.

2. Description of Service
NukeTracker helps users track players and tribe activity in ARK: Survival Ascended. It offers a Free version (includes ads) and a Premium version (ad-free, with additional features).

3. User Conduct
You agree not to misuse the bot or attempt to disrupt its functionality.

Do not use NukeTracker for harassment, stalking, or any form of malicious behavior.

4. Ads and Monetization
The Free version of NukeTracker may display in-bot ads or promotional messages.

You can upgrade to the Premium version to remove ads and access bonus features.

5. Availability
We strive to maintain 24/7 uptime, but we do not guarantee uninterrupted service. Downtime may occur for updates, bugs, or maintenance.

6. Termination
We reserve the right to block, ban, or remove NukeTracker from any server at our discretion, especially for abuse or violation of these terms.

7. Disclaimer
NukeTracker is not affiliated with or endorsed by Studio Wildcard or ARK: Survival Ascended. All ARK-related content belongs to their respective owners.
